  24Oct 2023: Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.6.0.1.ebuild
  Minor fix to url grabber to autocorrect htts:// to https://

  13Dec 2022: Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.6.0.ebuild
  Adds timestamp bracket (starttime/endtime) option to /replay command

  04Jul 2022: Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.5.2-r2.ebuild
  Remove erroneous 'dobin ICB.pm' instruction

  04Jul 2022: Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.5.2-r1.ebuild
  Remove dev-perl/Net-ICB from dependency list

  03Jul 2022: Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.5.2.ebuild
  Package ICB.pm now repackaged with icbm since dev-perl/Net-ICB is long
  defunct as a package.  It is installed in /usr/share/ic/Net.
  Update ebuild to EAPI=7
  
  19Jan 2020: Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.5.1.ebuild
  Add compatibility features for x11-terms/alacritty
  Set report_url_capture off by default

  08 Oct 2019: Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.12.ebuild
  Implement the URL hook type.  URL hook functions receive an abbreviated
  packet for each URL token in a message.

  22 Feb 2018: Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.11.ebuild
  Minor fix to the URL grabber tokenizer regex.

  07 Apr 2017; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.10-r1.ebuild:

  22 Apr 2016; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.10.ebuild:

  07 Mar 2016; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.9-r1.ebuild:
  Revise ebuild to reflect name change from dev-perl/math-pari to dev-perl/Math-Pari

  07 Mar 2016; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.9.ebuild:
  Convert from dev-perl/Crypt-DH to dev-perl/Crypt-DH-GMP

  07 Mar 2016; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.8.4-r1.ebuild:
  Revise ebuild to reflect name changes to dev-perl/crypt* ebuilds

  27 JUL 2015; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.8.4.ebuild:
  Fix several potential pointer overruns in talk()

  17 FEB 2015; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net> icbm-1.4.8.3.ebuild:
  Fix incorrect current nick reported at the remote end by /revoke

  17 FEB 2015; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>:
  Initial overlay creation.  Ebuild submitted by Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>
